Dancing with the Stars - Season 19, Episode 2




What a difference a night of Dancing makes! After what was surely a nervous night for some of our contestants, everyone was back in the ballroom again for some incredible performances from musical legends Smokey Robinson and Aloe Blacc! To make things even better, the three new pros: Keo Motsepe, Allison Holker and Artem Chigvintsev performed a sizzling routine together. It was set to be another unforgettable night in the ballroom, and especially memorable for one couple as someone faced elimination!




Original Air Date: 16-Sep-2014
